#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:2
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "故障排除"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:4
msgid ""
"This page provides some common troubles and their solutions. Besides, If "
"you encounter some runtime error that is hard to understand, you can "
"check the following list for help."
msgstr ""
"本页面提供了一些常见问题及其解决方案。"
"此外，如果您遇到难以理解的运行时错误，可以查看以下列表寻求帮助。"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:8
msgid "1. Duplicate Methods/Functions"
msgstr "1. 重复的方法/函数"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:10
msgid ""
"You may see words like ``ALREADY_REGISTERED`` being reported by message "
"callback. This is caused by registering a method/function for the second "
"time. A common cause is registering something manually after calling a "
"helper for generating registered functions/methods/behaviours. For "
"example, the code manually registers default constructor/copy "
"constructor/assignment operator (``opAssign``)/destructor after using "
"``behaviours_by_traits()``, which will register the above behaviours."
msgstr ""
"您可能会看到消息回调报告 ``ALREADY_REGISTERED`` 之类的提示。"
"这是由于重复注册方法/函数造成的。"
"常见原因是在调用生成已注册函数/方法/行为的辅助函数之后，"
"又手动注册了某些内容。"
"例如，在使用 ``behaviours_by_traits()``（它会注册上述行为）后，"
"又手动注册默认构造函数/复制构造函数/赋值运算符（``opAssign``）/析构函数。"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:14
msgid "2. Mismatched Function Signature"
msgstr "2. 函数签名不匹配"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:16
msgid ""
"Please check carefully the function signature in AngelScript and C++ are "
"perfectly matched. Especially when dealing with platform-dependent types,"
" for example, ``size_t``. Besides, a common mistake may be registering a "
"function accepting ``const char*`` / ``std::string_view`` as accepting "
"``string`` as its argument. You can create a wrapper function, or "
"register them by lambda."
msgstr ""
"请仔细检查 AngelScript 和 C++ 中的函数签名是否完全匹配。"
"特别是在处理平台相关类型时，例如 ``size_t``。"
"此外，一个常见错误是将接受 ``const char*`` / ``std::string_view`` 的函数注册为接受 "
"``string`` 作为参数。您可以创建一个包装函数，或通过 lambda 注册它们。"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:19
msgid "3. Invalid Type Flags for Value Type"
msgstr "3. 值类型的无效类型标志"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:21
#, python-format
msgid ""
"AngelScript needs a precise type information to use a value type in "
"native calling convention. Please check the official document for "
"details. A common mistake is forgetting to set "
"``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_MORE_CONSTRUCTORS`` before registering constructors "
"other than default/copy constructor. If you think the problem is caused "
"by the native calling convention and is hard to fix, you can try to force"
" ``asbind20`` to register all things in generic mode, as described at "
":ref:`here <group-force-generic>`. If switching to generic mode fixes "
"your problem, you can be 90% sure the problem is caused by invalid type "
"flags."
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 需要精确的类型信息才能在本机调用约定中使用值类型。"
"请查看官方文档以了解详情。"
"一个常见错误是在注册默认/复制构造函数以外的构造函数之前忘记设置 "
"``asOBJ_APP_CLASS_MORE_CONSTRUCTORS``。"
"如果您认为问题是由本机调用约定引起的且难以修复，"
"可以尝试强制 ``asbind20`` 以通用模式注册所有内容，"
"如 :ref:`此处 <group-force-generic>` 所述。"
"如果切换到通用模式解决了您的问题，"
"您可以 90% 确定问题是由无效的类型标志引起的。"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:25
msgid "Note for Windows + MSVC User"
msgstr "Windows + MSVC 用户注意事项"

#: ../../doc/extra/troubleshooting.rst:27
msgid ""
"If you see something like \"SEH exception with code 0xC0000005\", try the"
" solution in 2 and 3."
msgstr ""
"如果您看到类似 \"SEH exception with code 0xC0000005\" 的信息，"
"请尝试解决方案 2 和 3。"

